<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Sizzle Shack | Smash Burgers & Loaded Fries</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #ff4757;
            --secondary: #ffa502;
            --dark: #2f3542;
            --light: #f1f2f6;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        /* Header & Navigation */
        header {
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 15px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561758033-d89a9ad46330?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff2e44;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Menu Highlights */
        .menu-section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--secondary);
            margin: 10px auto 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .menu-item {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .menu-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .menu-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .menu-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .menu-info h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .menu-info p {
            color: #747d8c;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .menu-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .price {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Find Us Section */
        .info-section {
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .info-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ced6e0;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #1e222b;
            color: #a4b0be;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            .hero p { font-size: 16px; }
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* Kept simple for raw HTML/CSS */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">Sizzle<span>Shack</span></div>
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
                <a href="#about">Our Stall</a>
                <a href="#find-us">Find Us</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Hot, Fresh & Fast</h1>
        <p>Serving up the juiciest smash burgers and crispiest loaded fries in town. Made to order, served in minutes.</p>
        <a href="#menu" class="btn">View Our Menu</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Menu Section -->
    <section class="menu-section" id="menu">
        <h2 class="section-title">Stall Favorites</h2>
        <div class="menu-grid">
            
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Classic Smash Burger" class="menu-img">
                <div class="menu-info">
                    <h3>The Classic Smash</h3>
                    <p>Two smashed beef patties, melted American cheese, pickles, and our signature shack sauce on a toasted brioche bun.</p>
                    <div class="menu-footer">
                        <span class="price">$8.50</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573080496219-bb080dd4f877?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Loaded Cheese Fries" class="menu-img">
                <div class="menu-info">
                    <h3>Chili Cheese Fries</h3>
                    <p>Crispy golden fries smothered in house-made beef chili, warm cheddar cheese sauce, and topped with fresh jalapeños.</p>
                    <div class="menu-footer">
                        <span class="price">$6.00</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626082927389-6cd097cdc6ec?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Spicy Chicken Tenders" class="menu-img">
                <div class="menu-info">
                    <h3>Nashville Hot Tenders</h3>
                    <p>Three crispy buttermilk chicken tenders tossed in our fiery hot spice blend. Served with a side of creamy ranch.</p>
                    <div class="menu-footer">
                        <span class="price">$7.50</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Info Section -->
    <section class="info-section" id="find-us">
        <div class="info-container">
            <div class="info-box" id="about">
                <h3>Our Story</h3>
                <p>We started with a simple mission: bring restaurant-quality fast food to the streets. No frills, no fuss, just fresh ingredients and high heat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Location & Hours</h3>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> Corner of 4th & Main Street (Next to the central plaza)</p>
                <p><strong>Tuesday - Sunday:</strong> 12:00 PM - 10:00 PM</p>
                <p><strong>Monday:</strong> Closed for restructuring greatness</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Quick Orders</h3>
                <p>Skip the queue! Call or text your order ahead for fast pickup.</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 The Sizzle Shack. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
